# 📧 ChatGPT-Free Email Writer (Python)

This is a lightweight email writer tool built using Python and a free open-source AI model from Hugging Face. It automatically generates professional emails based on your input.

## 💡 Features

- Accepts any email topic from the user
- Automatically generates a professional email draft
- Saves the generated email into a `.txt` file
- Runs entirely offline — no OpenAI API key required!

## ⚙️ How It Works

1. The user is prompted to enter the purpose of the email (e.g., "follow up with a client").
2. The model generates a professional-sounding email using a text generation model.
3. The email is displayed and saved as `generated_email.txt`.

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Python
- Hugging Face `transformers`
- `distilgpt2` language model

